Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those who possess human bodies to take life in this dimension,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Geists are violent life forms who have traveled from another dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}During her battle with Slug Geist,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shion, a Doll, was rescued by the legendary leader of the Geists.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wolf Geist was created from the possession of Asaki Hiroki,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an ordinary high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though he was transforming into the Geist,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiroki still maintained his human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shion started to fall in love with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that night, Shion gave herself to Hiroki, body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next day Hiroki was called into the infirmary by Misuzu-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and was injected with a venom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that would fully transform him into Geist form in 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yukiko turned out to be a Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will Hiroki turn completely into a Geist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And who are the mysterious group of people who arrived on the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The mysteiy-filled story is now reaching its climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Single Figure who came to this dimension with that Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That Doll"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who raped 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not give you the answer for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However... If you defeat me, you will know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However I'm not finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to show you a really fun time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice, very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel more pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put you in the same position as that other Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hiroki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroki... You're still Hiroki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vol.04   The Fallen Demon Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lilium!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're gonna kill your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been violated so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her rejuvenation program won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Shion, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will trade my armor with her now. It has been damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't... Doesn't that mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were created to destroy Geists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must use any means necessary to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just washing the dirt from my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have my lenses soiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... Lilium!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill me now, you won't be able to prevent\NAsaki-kun from turning fully into a Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over the antidote at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I will give you an easy death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you say that line out of professionalism?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or out of jealousy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroki! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, just stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-sensei, what're you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill the two of you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing such an act in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, Misuzu-sensei was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will punish you at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just injected his body with the antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The venom that my scanner was picking up is gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not up to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witnessing that last battle gave me an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understanding of the fact that even if you turn into a\Nfull-fledged Geist, I wouldn't be able to control you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I changed my mind and decided to release you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll live as his slave from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way seems more appealing anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Hiroki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but that's... How shall I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but won't you come along too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting on airs is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cheeks are telling me you can't live without Hiroki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So Dolls can make that expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get along well as fellow slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stands at the top of all the Dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is our Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7, you surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought a Geist would poison your judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroki may have been infected by a Geist, but his heart is still human!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is different from the other Geists!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even Single Figures can be deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the power the leader of the Geists has?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body won't... move...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7, we will reinvestigate your case later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This barrier was created from a sample of your own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stronger you struggle, the stronger the barrier will become.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7, I want you to get a good look at this Geist's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity... Stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To your own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Geist infected me, my number was already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I was meant to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However you don't have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So live for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your heart is still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were programmed with the mission to\Nexterminate humans who have been infected by Geists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't... Hiroki... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Leader of the Geists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Shion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was my controlling program... ineffective on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that power come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency command sequence initiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency program initiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phase two initiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to a realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Just hold me without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, that makes me jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I was pierced, I injected my own body with a healing venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty close to dying, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However you... You betrayed your friends to protect a Geist, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Hiroki is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shion, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However since you've both already gone this far, I'll\Nneed to request your assistance in helping me fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As fellow slaves of Asaki-kun, let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help, too, so let me join in!
