Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.66,0:25:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't need memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.66,0:25:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}omoide wa iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.42,0:25:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}friendship or bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.42,0:25:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yuujou mo kizuna mo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I won't miss it if I throw it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}subete nage dashite mo oshiku wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.42,0:25:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Infinity...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.63,0:25:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I have unforgivable feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yurusarenu omoi mo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.30,0:25:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.01,0:25:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but if I live for your sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.80,0:25:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}anata no tame nara ba
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.88,0:25:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.59,0:26:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Are you surprised I survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.47,0:26:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I believe I can pierce through those feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.47,0:26:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}tsuranuite yukeru to shinjirareta
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.39,0:26:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It was within my grasp,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.39,0:26:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kono te no naka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.31,0:26:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I was built to aid the rebirth of the Wolf Geist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.14,0:26:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but the dreams slip through my fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.14,0:26:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}tsukanda hazu no yume ga kieteku
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.23,0:26:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– So until that happens, I cannot die.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.19,0:26:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}as if they're floating to a land long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.19,0:26:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}maru de hakanai utakata no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.40,0:26:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Just the mere fact that I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.40,0:26:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}anata o aishite iru koto dake ga
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.33,0:26:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}is proof enough that I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.33,0:26:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}watashi no ikita akashi
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.33,0:26:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My last wish is one and only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.33,0:26:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}saigo no negai wa tada hitotsu dake
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.71,0:26:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.25,0:26:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– That you lost your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.84,0:26:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please don't even forget that I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.84,0:26:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ai shita koto zettai ni wasurenai de
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.84,0:26:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Did you want to say something, Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.56,0:26:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Our love is being tom apart and hidden by the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.56,0:26:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kurayami de mienai hikisakareru ai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.23,0:26:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Even if we search for an exit, we will not find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.23,0:26:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}deguchi o sagashitara ari wa shinai
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.94,0:26:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– What is it, Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.10,0:27:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As if to mock us as we search for each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.10,0:27:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}motome au futari o azawarau ka you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.07,0:27:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}the wheel of fate begins to spin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.07,0:27:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}unmei no wa ga mata mawari dashita
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.54,0:27:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Hiroki...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.08,0:27:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The arms that once guided me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.08,0:27:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yasashii ude ni tsurarete ita
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.71,0:27:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I will kill him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.96,0:27:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}are left behind by time,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.96,0:27:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}toki wa sugita no
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.67,0:27:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and there is nothing left for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.67,0:27:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}watashi ni wa mou nani mo nai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.72,0:27:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Does that make you sad, Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll keep my unattainable vow locked in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kanawanai chikai kokoro ni himete
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.06,0:27:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and let go of my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.06,0:27:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ashita sae tebanashite
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.85,0:27:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– You useless Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.10,0:27:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Even if it's a fight I have no right in winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.10,0:27:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kateru sube nado nai tatakai demo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.65,0:27:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}fasing it head on is the only choice I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.65,0:27:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}tachimukau shika mou michi wa nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.61,0:27:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Nee-san. I won't deliver the final blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.91,0:27:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The world is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.91,0:27:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}owaru sekai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.91,0:27:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Traitors should die slowly and painfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.87,0:27:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Farewell, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.87,0:27:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I put my faith in us,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.87,0:27:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}futari o kakeru ga
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.46,0:27:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but the whiteness is all that reaches to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.46,0:27:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}shiroku sashinoberu
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.46,0:27:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Hiroki... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.50,0:28:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For now...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.50,0:28:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ima wa
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.25,0:28:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I can't be... with you anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.51,0:28:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I... will... disappear... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.27,0:28:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– So...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.94,0:28:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Just the mere fact that I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.94,0:28:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}anata o aishite iru koto dake ga
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.99,0:28:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}– Just the mere fact that I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.86,0:28:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}is proof enough that I lived.
